data.description: Discover the perfect blend of location, price, and comfort in this 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath home. Nestled on a corner lot, on a quiet street, you'll find mature shade trees and a fenced backyard with both chain link and wood fencing, complete with a  storage shed. Inside, the open floor plan offers a spacious living room with  carpeting, a ceiling fan, and a wood-burning fireplace with stone surround. The kitchen/dining room combo boasts vinyl tile flooring, solid countertops, an  breakfast bar, and a gas range oven. Located in Flood Zone X, requiring no Flood Insurance! Don't miss your chance – schedule a private showing today!
